data.description: Located in the iconic area of Grey Forest, a unique and original cottage style home situated adjacent to the historic spring-fed swimming hole of Helotes Creek. This lovely home sits on almost one acre of land and backs up to a private greenbelt, the home is surrounded by majestic oak mature trees creating a canopy over the home. The adorable original door is the perfect entry point, along with the rock walls and vaulted ceilings that conclude to the rarity this home possesses. Old meets NEW as you enter the KITCHEN!!!  Kitchen remodel includes incredible backsplash, a new sub floor and insulation with a new raised ceiling. Kitchen boasts quartz and butcher block countertops, custom cabinets with pull out trash (fascinating) high-end appliances, dishwasher drawer, microwave drawer, new electrical and plumbing including a new gas line for the range. Amazing NEW walk in pantry with NEW custom soft close cabinetry, that include a very unique pull out cabinet specific for a cake mixer (super COOL) new built WALK-IN BUTLERS PANTRY, with additional storage and work space. MUST SEE newly renovated master bathroom and secondary bathroom, unique tile used for flooring throughout along with soft close custom cabinetry and quartz countertops, with KOHLER faucets that help create that modern appeal. Step outside and choose from several sitting areas that this home has to offer. When you venture you will find a cool hand dug well that you can create a wishing well out of, also outside you'll enjoy the other 1/2 acre where the old original barn is, this barn has served as a work area, additional storage, or a carport. Bring your RV or your boat, they can be stowed away here. Back inside there are three oversized bedrooms, new finished out closets that offer more storage/space, and one of the bedrooms can also be split into an office, these bedrooms are extremely unique in space. Refrigerator, washer and dryer convey. New window shutters convey too. This HOME is a MUST SEE, please bring your BUYERS.
